data.description: Welcome to this charming 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home located in the heart of New Braunfels, Texas. Boasting an impressive 2188 square feet of spacious living area, this property comfortably caters to modern family living. The home's fluid layout includes an office area, perfect for remote work or studying. Each of the four bedrooms is generously sized, ensuring plenty of room for everyone. The corner lot location offers additional privacy and space, making it a perfect haven for enjoying the outdoors. This property seamlessly blends comfort, convenience, and charm, offering an unrivaled living experience in a desirable Texas locale. Don't miss out on this opportunity to own a piece of New Braunfels charm. The sellers are offering up to $500 for a home warranty and up to 2% of the contract price in closing cost/rate buydown assistance.
